    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I am so excited to show you this absolute gem! Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible condition that it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it\u2019s been kept in pristine shape\u2014not a scratch or a worry to be found! It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for that brand-new feel without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve gotta come see this one. Drop me a message and let's get you behind the wheel!",
