    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S54 platform, featuring individual throttle bodies and a precision-tuned dual-VANOS system. The 3.2L straight-six delivers a linear power band to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual and a limited-slip differential. Mechanically pristine, the vehicle has undergone a comprehensive subframe reinforcement and a recent valve adjustment to ensure peak volumetric efficiency. The suspension geometry remains factory-perfect, providing the tactile feedback and lateral grip these chassis are renowned for. With a documented service history focusing on preventative maintenance and fluid analysis, this vehicle offers an uncompromised driving experience for the technical purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
