      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Experience the pinnacle of automotive preservation with this showroom-quality masterpiece. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one, appearing exactly as it did on the dealership floor. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather seats show no signs of wear, the dashboard is free of any sun exposure, and every electronic component functions with factory precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history from certified technicians and incredibly low mileage. No accidents, no modifications, and a smoke-free/pet-free history. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a truly flawless example of this model. Includes all original manuals, two sets of keys, and a custom car cover.",
      "price": 48500.0,
